data.value:
Welcome to Warmarts' Raffle Drawing Program.
This program allows the individual running the raffle to simplify their life.
The program REQUIRES the person running it to be connected to the internet. The data is stored in an online SQL Server database.
To run the program, all the user has to do is put in the name of the ticket buyer and the quantity of tickets purchased, no bonus tickets as this program will automatically calculate that. Once that is done, pressing the "Submit Purchase" button will submit the ticket drawing to the online database.
Pressing "Cancel Purchase" prior to submitting purchase will clear the form and not submit any data.
Running the raffle is as simple as pressing the "Run Drawing" button. This will open a new window with the raffle results, a total of eight (8) winners with a d6 random number next to their name. This also generates an additional (X) number of winners of bonus prizes.
----AFTER THE RAFFLE IS RUN---- The database will need to be cleared after the raffle is run. To perform this task, simpliy click on the File menu and select "Clear Database" from the menu. *****WARNING***** DO NOT DO THIS UNTIL *AFTER* THE RAFFLE IS RUN. THIS WILL WIPE ALL DATA FROM DATABASE WITH NO RECOVERY POSSIBLE!!!!
